  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras/dc98e8e0f5ab53bcb9d1384af5a5beda.poster.avif?t=1737635374\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras/dc98e8e0f5ab53bcb9d1384af5a5beda.webm?t=1737635374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras/dc98e8e0f5ab53bcb9d1384af5a5beda.mp4?t=1737635374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bananitro </strong>is a 2D runner game that combines speed and action with a unique gravity mechanic. Winner of the \"Monkey Jam 2024,\" <strong>Bananitro </strong>innovatively brings together monkeys and bicycles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RUN TO WIN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controlling Monkey on his bicycle, use <strong>Bananitro </strong>to reach incredible speeds, ride on walls, perform maneuvers, and make spectacular jumps that defy the laws of gravity. But be careful, each track is unique and full of obstacles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLEASH YOUR CREATIVITY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t be afraid to race in your own style. Whether fast and cautious, speedy and daring, or completely improvised, in <strong>Bananitro</strong>, creativity is the key to finishing the races.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras/2e7c31ae0fad1d6f10b1d31097af7ebc.avif?t=1737635374\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras_big/2e7c31ae0fad1d6f10b1d31097af7ebc.avif?t=1737635374 width=800 height=777 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras/dc98e8e0f5ab53bcb9d1384af5a5beda.poster.avif?t=1737635374\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras/dc98e8e0f5ab53bcb9d1384af5a5beda.webm?t=1737635374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras/dc98e8e0f5ab53bcb9d1384af5a5beda.mp4?t=1737635374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bananitro </strong>is a 2D runner game that combines speed and action with a unique gravity mechanic. Winner of the \"Monkey Jam 2024,\" <strong>Bananitro </strong>innovatively brings together monkeys and bicycles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RUN TO WIN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controlling Monkey on his bicycle, use <strong>Bananitro </strong>to reach incredible speeds, ride on walls, perform maneuvers, and make spectacular jumps that defy the laws of gravity. But be careful, each track is unique and full of obstacles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLEASH YOUR CREATIVITY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t be afraid to race in your own style. Whether fast and cautious, speedy and daring, or completely improvised, in <strong>Bananitro</strong>, creativity is the key to finishing the races.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras/2e7c31ae0fad1d6f10b1d31097af7ebc.avif?t=1737635374\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141340/extras_big/2e7c31ae0fad1d6f10b1d31097af7ebc.avif?t=1737635374 width=800 height=777 /></span></p>",
